    body
      // Header
      header
        .container
            .divider
                .logo
                    a(href="../").logo
                        span Talk Push Logo
                    a(href="#").menu-button
                        i(class="fa fa-bars",aria-hidden="true")
                .menu
                    include ../../jade/_navigation.jade
      
      .display-header.augmented-recruiter
        .filter
          .container
            .augmented-header
              .video
                .video-holder
                  iframe(width='560', height='315', src='https://www.youtube.com/embed/abg2U9DuAiA', frameborder='0', allowfullscreen='')
              .header-text
                h1 Augmented Recruiter
                p Every month, we feature recruiters who embrace automation in our Augmented Recruiters Series.
                p This month we feature Ping Catalina from Alexander Mann Solutions.
      .white-holder.equal.white-theme
        .container
          .augmented-display: img(src="../images/augmented-page/display.jpg", alt="Augmented Recruiter")
          h2.augmented-name 5 Facts about Ping Sta. Catalina
          hr.augmented-line
          h3.augmented-title Hello please can you tell me your position/speciality in recruitment?
          p.augmented-body I am Ping Sta. Catalina and I am a recruiting manager for Alexander Mann Solutions.
          hr.augmented-line
          h3.augmented-title What was it like to source and look for candidates before Talkpush?
          p.augmented-body Before Talkpush, it was pretty challenging because we are only using traditional sourcing channel.
          hr.augmented-line
          h3.augmented-title What's the advantage of using technology and Social Media to attract more candidates?
          p.augmented-body When we use technology and social media, we are able to tap a bigger market and we are able to tap candidates who may not be interested in another opportunity for now but we are able to convert them.
          hr.augmented-line
          h3.augmented-title Do you think that this technology may affect the type of profiles you hire?
          p.augmented-body This technology basically allows us to tap profiles who are targeted and who are specifically what our account we looking for.
          hr.augmented-line
          h3.augmented-title Is there a new portion of the talent pool that you are trying to access by using Talkpush?
          p.augmented-body Talkpush allows you to reach out even to pass every dormant candidates and even they are not available within the office hours we are able to reach them after we finish our shift.
                      
